%% seq_02b_task_status_assignment.mmd
%% Scope: Assignment and task status execution flow.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Project Member / Manager
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Entity as TaskEntity
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: ASSIGN TASK
    U->>B: Update assignee
    B->>C: PUT /tasks/:id
    C->>Cmd: UpdateTaskCommand -> AssignTaskCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: findById(taskId)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT task
    Repo-->>Cmd: Task aggregate
    Cmd->>Entity: assignTo(userId)
    Cmd->>Repo: save(task)
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE tasks.assigned_to
    Cmd->>Evt: emit(task:assigned)
    C-->>B: Return updated task

    Note over U, Evt: CHANGE STATUS
    U->>B: Change task status
    B->>C: PUT /tasks/:id/status
    C->>Cmd: UpdateTaskStatusCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: findById(taskId)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT task
    Repo-->>Cmd: Task aggregate
    Cmd->>Entity: Validate transition and guards

    alt todo -> in_progress without assignee
        Cmd-->>C: Reject request
        C-->>B: 422 validation error
    else Valid transition
        Cmd->>Repo: save(task)
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE tasks.status
        Cmd->>Evt: emit(task:status:changed)
        Note over Evt: done-category transition also triggers review-session setup
        C-->>B: Return updated task
    end
